snippet.title: Amber Alert
snippet.description:
Amber alert that went out for 2 missg kids. Milwaukee, Wisconsin.

UPDATE FEBRUARY 18TH 2020: Woman and children were found dead Sunday, February 16th inside a garage on 47th and Burleigh in Milwaukee. Ex boyfriend, Arzel Avery, was turnef in by father and is in Memphis, Tennessee, will be extradited back to Milwaukee.  Neighbor heard the struggle and heard woman yelling for help, finally saying please don't kill me and everything went silent. When police went to investigate, they claimed they couldn't find the 911 caller. Amarah Banks was strangled and Avery attempted to burn the bodies after an argument.

News Article:



https://www.wisn.com/article/milwaukee-suspect-says-he-strangled-mom-kisds-tried-to-burn-bodies/30972981
